captions.text:
The next game is "Parallel Reality",
with Daniel and Cris.
Our players will start a scene

and whenever we want
to see a parallel reality,

or to see a scene happening
in a different way,

we'll go back in time and change
everything that happened.

For that, I'll need a place
for the scene to start.
'Labyrinth'?

'Labyrinth' is the place where
"Parallel Reality" begins, now!
'Minotaur'.

Wow, Minotaur...
Your labyrinth is wonderful!
But I need to be rescued!

All virgins complain about my
labyrinth! This is where you'll stay!

- I know that Perseus or Penteus...
- I don't want to hear about Perseus!

He will save me, okay?
He will! Perseus! Perseus?

I hear the voice that will
lead me to the damned!
Perseus! Perseus!

- Stop, stop!
- Keep calling me!

- Oh, my God! - I know this
labyrinth like the back of my...

- Paw!
- Paw!

Know that this sword will
finish you for good...
I'm dead!
No...

Back to the moment when
Perseus draws his sword!
With this sword...
I have one too!

- How did you get this sword... Saber...
- Because I'm your father!

Back to the moment when
Perseus enters the labyrinth.
Perseus!
Good thing I have a GPS.
Silence!

Welcome to the labyrinth,
do you have a reservation?

No, I have a GPS,
I'll get there in a second!

- You'd rather go with a GPS, then?
- I'll go with the GPS.

- I can't trust...
- You can turn left there, thank you.

- You forgot your sword...
- Mr. Mino...
Sir? Sir?

- Minotaur!
- How did you find me?

- I have a GPS!
- Yes! He has a GPS!
Know that...

Back to the moment when the
Minotaur enters the labyrinth with her.

- And this is the living room!
- How sweet!

- Your house is like a labyrinth!
- Oh, stop... Do you want a drink?
Yes, of course!

You know, Gise... I can't figure
out if you're a virgin or not...
Do you want milk?
You know I'm 13, right?

Wait a minute,
the phone is ringing.
This is Mino, hello?

Mr. Minotaur, there's a
mr. Perseus here for you.

- Perseus?
- Perseus? No, no, no!
He's the cable guy, send him up.

- He's going up.
- Okay, thank you!

Not Perseus, man! The cable guy
is my boyfriend! Cut it out, man!

- Boyfriend? What are you talking about?
- I can explain it, Perseus, I...

- Explain?
- Do you know each other?

- Yes!
- Yes! What are you doing here?

In the house of this horse...
Half horse...
Minotaur.
Don't mock me...

Back to the moment when the
Minotaur asks if she's a virgin.
Are you a Sagittarius?

- No...
- Sagittarius, got it?

Yeah, yeah...
No, I'm a Virgo.

- Perfect!
- I know... With Taurus rising!
Moon in Scorpio...

- You're making Taurus
rise, girl... - Yeah...
What a weird statue you have!

- You're so smart, baby!
- Yeah, I'm a Sagittarius! No, Virgo!
You're the Sagittarius!

When you can't tell a statue from
a dead person, that's so Sagittarius!

- Because everybody puts statues
in the closet! - Of course!

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented
